internal opacapi	  	      compiler/opacapi
internal libopa 	  	      compiler/opa

internal opabsl_for_compiler	      lib/opabsl
internal opabsl_for_server	      lib/opabsl
internal opabsl_for_interpreter       lib/opabsl
